rComments: I went into the course with very low interest, but left with complete different perspective. Amazing lectures by Prof. Ward. She also has a good sense of humor. Would take the course again.

AMAZING lectures, super-informative, funny and you will learn a ton! If you get a chance to take one of her classes do not miss the chance! Easily one of the best lecturers I've ever had. Obviously very passionate about the material and has great content.
